00:23:08.040 --> 00:23:15.300
from 1831 and was written
by Samuel Goodrich.

00:23:15.300 --> 00:23:23.850 position:56%
So Samuel Griswold Goodrich was born
in August 1793 and died in May 1860

00:23:23.850 --> 00:23:28.050
and he was an American
bookseller and publisher and editor

00:23:28.050 --> 00:23:30.960
and a writer and among the
first Americans who wrote

00:23:30.960 --> 00:23:34.660
and published books for American
children and young adults.

00:23:34.660 --> 00:23:38.120
Previous children's books had not
been written in the United States,

00:23:38.120 --> 00:23:40.510
but instead been imported
from Britain and Europe

00:23:40.510 --> 00:23:44.180
and for the most part, been
written by British authors.

00:23:44.180 --> 00:23:47.330
Goodrich was responsible for
the publications of dozens

00:23:47.330 --> 00:23:51.840
of works ranging from pocket-size
chapbooks to massive geographies

00:23:51.840 --> 00:23:54.820
and according to the Boston
Globe sold 6 million copies

00:23:54.820 --> 00:23:56.950
of his various books in total.

00:23:56.950 --> 00:24:01.170
His most famous creation is
