and various other subjects.

00:24:19.670 --> 00:24:23.550 position:56%
Thus teaching the fictive children
in the books while entertaining them

00:24:23.550 --> 00:24:26.880
and also the real children who
are reading them are being taught

00:24:26.880 --> 00:24:29.690
and hopefully entertained
at the same time.

00:24:29.690 --> 00:24:32.890
The book we're going to be looking
