00:25:09.920 --> 00:25:12.130
But first let's see what
Goodrich actually has

00:25:12.130 --> 00:25:15.230
to say about the earth in 1836.

00:25:15.230 --> 00:25:20.990
So I'm going to read the text for
you, so just look at the picture.

00:25:20.990 --> 00:25:25.050
This says chapter 4, Parley
